22:17.701 --> 22:22.172
All right, vila,
there's only room in this shop
for one of us.

22:22.173 --> 22:25.308
Go for
your carpenter's square.

22:35.886 --> 22:39.523
That's pretty fancy shooting
there, partner.

22:39.524 --> 22:41.958
Not a mark on him.

22:43.661 --> 22:44.994
Defective gun, al.

22:55.439 --> 22:58.508
<i>(woman)</i> 5, 4, 3, 2...

23:01.212 --> 23:03.380
Just get through this.
Ok.

23:03.381 --> 23:04.614
Great.

23:05.683 --> 23:07.584
So, jill...

23:07.585 --> 23:10.019
I'm sorry.

23:12.056 --> 23:13.022
Great.
